('When God Bless America Replaces Thy Kingdom Come', 'James Bell', 'How Patriotism Became Our Practical Savior. A direct examination of how patriotism has replaced the kingdom of God as the practical savior in American Christianity.', 'authored', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
