('The Most Dangerous Person on a Church Staff (It Might Surprise You)', 'most-dangerous-person-church-staff', 'From the PCN Articles Library: Not all staff problems are obvious. This article explores the hidden dynamics that can undermine a healthy staff culture.', 'Leadership Formation', '8 min', true, NOW()),
