('What the Church in the Global South Can Teach the Church in America About Suffering', 'global-south-church-teach-suffering', 'From the PCN Articles Library: The persecuted church has wisdom about faith that the comfortable church needs. This article explores what that wisdom is.', 'Leadership Formation', '8 min', true, NOW()),
